articles.title: NASA, ESA join forces on life-hunting ExoMars rover - Space.com
articles.description: NASA is stepping in for ExoMars' former partner, the Russian space agency Roscosmos.
articles.content:
Europe's long-delayed ExoMars rover mission to the Red Planet just got a boost for its projected launch in 2028.
